1
00:01:03,920 --> 00:01:04,879
Please wait a moment.

2
00:01:04,879 --> 00:01:07,810
Our chairman and general manager will be right here.

3
00:01:13,039 --> 00:01:13,920
How do you know

4
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:15,730
the chairman of Taichen Group?

5
00:01:16,320 --> 00:01:17,980
What if I said I don't know him?

6
00:01:18,720 --> 00:01:19,920
How is that possible?

7
00:01:20,440 --> 00:01:21,360
My dad said

8
00:01:21,720 --> 00:01:23,800
their chairman agreed to discuss cooperation

9
00:01:23,800 --> 00:01:24,840
as a favor to you.

10
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:30,120
He even specifically asked you to accompany me to discuss the investment.

11
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:31,450
I really don't know him.

12
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:34,520
Mr. Gu.

13
00:01:38,479 --> 00:01:39,400
Mr. Shi.

14
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:41,240
Mr. Gu,

15
00:01:41,720 --> 00:01:42,720
we meet again.

16
00:01:44,800 --> 00:01:46,600
And you said you didn't know her.

17
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,160
Chen Zixi.

18
00:01:49,960 --> 00:01:51,360
Did she not die back then?

19
00:01:51,479 --> 00:01:52,200
So Mr. Shi

20
00:01:52,320 --> 00:01:53,720
is the chairman of Taichen Group.

21
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:55,640
I failed to recognize someone of your importance yesterday.

22
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:56,160
Mr. Gu,

23
00:01:56,800 --> 00:01:57,880
our Taichen Group

24
00:01:58,039 --> 00:02:00,480
is also an industry leader in car manufacturing.

25
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:02,720
Originally, we weren't optimistic about Chen's Group,

26
00:02:02,720 --> 00:02:05,720
but my godfather is very grateful that you saved him yesterday

27
00:02:05,720 --> 00:02:08,440
and is willing to make an exception to cooperate with you.

28
00:02:08,440 --> 00:02:09,100
However...

29
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:12,440
Favors are favors.

30
00:02:12,760 --> 00:02:13,680
I am a businessman,

31
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:15,440
and investments cannot lose money.

32
00:02:15,440 --> 00:02:16,560
Chen's Group

33
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:19,360
needs to prove its strength in the racing field.

34
00:02:20,160 --> 00:02:21,160
How do we prove it?

35
00:02:22,160 --> 00:02:23,320
As long as you win

36
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:25,880
next month's XT Team Challenge,

37
00:02:26,079 --> 00:02:28,120
I will invest in Chen's Group.

38
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:31,760
XT Team Challenge?

39
00:02:31,880 --> 00:02:33,320
Although there are many strong competitors,

40
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:34,520
we are not bad either.

41
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:35,960
I needed to earn points

42
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:37,079
in various competitions anyway

43
00:02:37,079 --> 00:02:39,600
to have a chance to advance to the Dragon Country Grand Prix.

44
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:41,400
Isn't this a win-win situation?

45
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:42,720
All right.

46
00:02:43,040 --> 00:02:44,770
We will do as Chairman Shi says.

47
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:46,720
Great.

48
00:02:48,920 --> 00:02:50,050
Happy cooperation.

49
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:51,450
Happy cooperation.

50
00:02:51,760 --> 00:02:54,420
I look forward to your performance on the track.

51
00:02:57,760 --> 00:02:58,160
Okay.

52
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:02,620
That's wonderful.

53
00:03:03,480 --> 00:03:04,540
This is my fiancée,

54
00:03:04,760 --> 00:03:05,490
Chen Ziqing.

55
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:07,400
Nice to meet you.

56
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:07,880
Hello.

57
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:09,650
Let's go.

58
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:10,330
Let's go.

59
00:03:13,440 --> 00:03:14,440
Chen Ziqing.

60
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:16,880
Judging by the name,

61
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:20,760
could she be Zixi's twin sister?

62
00:03:26,720 --> 00:03:27,200
Come.

63
00:03:31,160 --> 00:03:33,200
This kid is really lucky.

64
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:36,020
He actually got involved with Chairman Shi.

65
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:37,900
As long as I'm here,

66
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:39,840
there's no way I'll let that kid

67
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,680
win the XT Challenge.

68
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:43,050
Mr. Ding,

69
00:03:44,040 --> 00:03:45,960
I don't mean to pour cold water on you,

70
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:46,880
but your skills

71
00:03:47,480 --> 00:03:48,610
compared to this kid

72
00:03:48,720 --> 00:03:49,980
are still a bit behind.

73
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:53,410
Then tell me,

74
00:03:54,079 --> 00:03:55,680
what should we do about this?

75
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:02,340
It's easy to dodge a spear in the open,

76
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:04,930
but hard to guard against an arrow in the dark.

77
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:06,090
Mr. Ding.

78
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:10,480
You can use some dirty tricks.

79
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:32,560
Shiqi,

80
00:04:32,760 --> 00:04:33,760
you and Baozi, come in.

81
00:04:33,760 --> 00:04:34,490
How about it?

82
00:04:34,760 --> 00:04:35,320
Captain,

83
00:04:35,760 --> 00:04:37,560
we haven't touched a car in years.

84
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:39,159
Are you still counting on us?

85
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:42,000
The XT Team Challenge requires a team to participate.

86
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,200
Each team needs three people.

87
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:44,520
Now Ziqing counts as one,

88
00:04:44,520 --> 00:04:45,920
we are still short of one.

89
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:48,880
I know a place

90
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:51,880
where we can get information about racers.

91
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:53,480
You mean

92
00:04:54,159 --> 00:04:54,880
Lan Bar?

93
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:00,600
Then I'll go check it out another day.

94
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:01,040
Sure,

95
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:02,020
go check it out.

96
00:05:16,400 --> 00:05:17,160
Enjoy your drink.

97
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:18,680
The boss will be here shortly.

98
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:19,080
Okay.

99
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:07,240
Mr. Gu,

100
00:06:07,880 --> 00:06:08,800
are you asleep?

101
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:09,720
Wake up.

102
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:12,520
The drug is quite strong.

103
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:15,760
Go away.

104
00:06:20,320 --> 00:06:22,040
The show is about to begin.

105
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:46,560
Hello,

106
00:06:47,520 --> 00:06:48,200
Miss Chen.

107
00:06:48,880 --> 00:06:50,400
I have good news for you.

108
00:06:54,080 --> 00:06:54,740
Who are you?

109
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:56,800
What good news?

110
00:06:58,280 --> 00:07:00,160
Your fiancé is at Lan Bar,

111
00:07:00,200 --> 00:07:02,400
spending the night with another woman.

112
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,480
If you go now,

113
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:05,450
you might catch them in the act.

114
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:10,360
Why should I believe you?

115
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:12,770
Look at the photo I sent you.

116
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:24,280
Gu Haoran.

117
00:07:24,840 --> 00:07:25,680
You are dead.

118
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:35,060
Having a lot of fun, are we?

119
00:07:35,640 --> 00:07:36,570
Sister Lan, I...

120
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:42,720
Plotting against my guests right under my nose?

121
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:45,810
Are you tired of living?

122
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:47,100
Sister Lan.

123
00:07:47,760 --> 00:07:48,800
I'm sorry, Sister Lan.

124
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:49,860
I won't do it again.

125
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:53,840
Who put you up to this?

126
00:07:54,840 --> 00:07:55,400
No one.

127
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:57,180
I just needed money lately

128
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:59,040
and wanted to extort some from Master Gu.

129
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:00,840
Playing mind games with me, huh?

130
00:08:01,120 --> 00:08:01,720
Fine.

131
00:08:02,080 --> 00:08:04,080
Since you like seducing men so much,

132
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:05,360
why don't you stay

133
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:07,730
and serve the brothers in the bar well?

134
00:08:08,160 --> 00:08:09,420
Thank you, Sister Lan.

135
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:10,860
Sister Lan.

136
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:11,800
I'll talk.

137
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:13,700
Master Ding told me to do this.

138
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:14,890
Please spare me.

139
00:08:15,440 --> 00:08:16,170
Are you sure?

140
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:17,530
I'm sure.

141
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:18,530
I'm sure.

142
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:20,360
Phone.

143
00:08:23,200 --> 00:08:24,000
Take her away.

144
00:08:24,200 --> 00:08:26,600
Record a clarification and apology video.

145
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:40,320
Handsome boy.

146
00:08:41,159 --> 00:08:43,080
You are too defenseless.

147
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:48,480
He Nan.

148
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:49,640
Snap out of it.

149
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:50,680
I'm so hot.

150
00:08:50,800 --> 00:08:52,000
You've been drugged.

151
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:57,600
I can't control myself.

152
00:08:59,480 --> 00:09:00,960
Now you like me?

153
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:06,520
Zixi.

154
00:09:07,160 --> 00:09:07,560
I...

155
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:09,450
I missed you so much.

156
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:16,760
Take a good look at who I am.
